Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaze Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it doesn't matter how many times you attack me. It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That lightning certainly is powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I shouldn't be taking {\i0}this{\i1} much damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ge-Ge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It just feels like the Share Energy within me is disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Negear, you should probably deactivate HDD.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but our Share reserves are dropping rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's charge up the Pong Laser nice and good again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we target this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people there, so it'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Lady Neptune is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Sis will save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nepgear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't have enough Share Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the gloomy look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainy Ratnapura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your so-called event?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit tacky, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Noire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vert too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You came?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply came here as 5pb's chauffeur.{to deliver 5pb}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Nepgear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,5pb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Uni.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go join Sis and the others, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do my part as well.{my part?}{i.e. also fight as much as i would've fought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that 5pb?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.32,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in our goddesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My, she certainly did dredge up something rather absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's apparently the CPU of Tari, the superpower of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't imagine how a nation that collapsed so long ago got its hands on so much Share Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden was using a similar device.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a machine that {\i1}creates{\i0} Share Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we should start by destroying it, should we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, four-on-one's a bit annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My powers are draining away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my Share Energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a device that {\i1}steals{\i0} Shares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the laser should be fully charged by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I push the big red button, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still gonna do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack from under the laser, and she can't hit you with her lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Blanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rom! Ram!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ram. The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the Share Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Histy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I calmed down and thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that everything made sense if Eden's machine could steal Shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you went and kept the best part all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's {\i1}our{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken enough Share Energy to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Destroy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you want this nation for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really want...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is to lay waste to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a CPU too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet all they did was bitch and whine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They never obeyed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"They"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tari cracked down on citizens that showed any discontent toward their CPU.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That made people lose faith in her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the nation eventually lost its Shares and collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The so-called "Great Tari Crash."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she reaped what she sowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They stole my nation from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, {\i1}I'll{\i0} be the one doing the stealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Recharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You never had any friends, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll offer you my sympathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can never have our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.26,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The world lies shattered into pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.38,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}But I don't need to pick up all the fragments
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with maximum output for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.35,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}There's only one that matters to me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your petty magic won't be able to stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.77,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My true love is all I need find
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Vert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Noire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.61,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Within the moonlit darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uni.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.90,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I stand alone, with my heart of stone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nepgear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your strength!{ugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:24.49,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Singing a song for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're just gonna try and destroy the Pong Laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.66,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My words don't take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.96,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}But music doesn't have any rights or wrongs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if you can pull it off before it finishes charging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:36.42,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It simply forms an irreplaceable bond
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:42.47,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll get stronger just by staying here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send ya flying there at the speed of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:51.35,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}For this is where I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you even aiming?{where do you think you're sending her}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.19,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The moment my faint voice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.07,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Reaches people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.36,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It will give them courage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't even tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.70,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}To overcome anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.24,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I play my heart out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of this, Sis!{sis pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.50,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My hard beat cannot be stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:18.75,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}May my song reach the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.43,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The moment my faint voice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.22,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Reaches people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:33.19,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It will give them courage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:36.61,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}To overcome anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's charged enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:45.61,Hard beat x Break beat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,500)\blur3}May my song echo across the world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got it out, I can cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My continent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What you desire will never come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to throw in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that sinking my continent{making it fall}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was all you needed to do to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I unleashed the energy I have left,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I could send half the world flying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The hatred is surprisingly strong in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, hatred is all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we use up all our Share Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one job we goddesses have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nepgear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, play hero all you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can blow {\i1}them{\i0} up, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll crush the world to bits and piec—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we have a problem.{i can't let you do that etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is gonna be {\i1}mine{\i0} someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All good, old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Off to the dark abyss of despair with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally got an anti-crystal back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but should we really have used it for this, old hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I decided it on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The "whimsical" trait only works for characters under twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always and forever be your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But just for today, let me express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bar Whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling a bar whore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.94,No fun allowed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,800)\fnCalisto MT\blur4.5\alpha&H33&\pos(960,417)}A Few Months Later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.94,No fun allowed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,800)\fnCalisto MT\blur0.9\pos(960,417)}A Few Months Later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your efforts, we recovered our Shares
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand here today to celebrate the completion of the new Planeptower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your Shares remained stable since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We merely had them stolen by Tari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We hadn't lost the trust of our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin the ceremony, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the time you attacked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like you'd taken advantage of our treaty of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and all I could see was red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, it was kinda fun fighting you all-out for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came up with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to your faith that we were able to complete the new Planeptower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of Planeptune is \Nrecovering by the day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As this nation's CPU, \NI'm grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take this opportunity to make an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I gotta do it in this form!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Neptune, Planeptune's CPU,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,declare the treaty of friendship null and void!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that old thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're true buddies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Noire, Vert, Blanc?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to compete fair and square from now on, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even you can be clever once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about we hold an exhibition match right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart's all aflutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:02.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}I've come to this universe of countless stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}To start our search for the ultimate game
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the protagonist here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}We're goddesses, the giga and tera
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uni!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}What are you getting so serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ram!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}You're in a trance. You've gone nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}I get you. I really do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.65,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}It's not love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:20.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}But there's desire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:24.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Here we go! Good to go, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna show them we're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:28.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Let's start a New Game+
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Here we go! Way to go, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:32.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}This rectangle pulse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}is a love song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things are going to get chaotic once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Here we go! Good to go, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:41.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Friendship, love, bifrost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:45.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}We're all friends, even if it's all a bit ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:51.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,750)\blur1.5}Good job, my sweet heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:57.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,750)\blur1.5}See you next week!
